des:
Listen to this Gizmo Girl story with a timeless lesson. 
Google encourages polyphasic sleep at work, Gizmo Girl learns from cats in this wilderness therapy session, where natural routines of sleep and eating are asynchronous and on demand, just like when we were little babies in natures care.
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
